Jenica Bergere was born on July 4, 1974. She is an actress and producer, known for Rat Race (2001), Frozen (2013) and Safety Not Guaranteed (2012). She has been married to Josh Jackson since August 3, 2002. They have one child.

Jenica /jeni-ca/ [3 sylls.] as a name for girls is of Hebrew and English origin, and the name Jenica means God is gracious. Jenica is a variant transcription of Jane (Hebrew): originally a feminine transcription of John. Jenica is also a variant of Jean (Hebrew). Jenica is also used as a variant of Jenny (English).
